            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;💡&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(200, 0, 143); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Tip:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt; To view all cases currently assigned to you, click &quot;Enquiries&quot; on the top-left, and choose the &quot;My Cases&quot;&amp;nbsp;list view filter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
